title: Lilyhammer S2 Ep7 - The Freezer
description:
Lilyhammer S2 Ep7 - The Freezer

The Freezer - Frank and Torgeir put the squeeze on a local farmer, who has been selling mislabelled meats to the Flamingo. Frank meets a charismatic young woman who enters the club. It takes him a moment to recognise her as Tiril, his son's pre-school teacher. Smitten, Frank approaches her and they strike a tone. After a few drinks, they leave together and spend the night at Frank's place. Meanwhile, Thomas Aune and Zlatan arrive in New York. They're escorted by a distant relative of Zlatan named Dino, who takes them to a known hangout for DeLucci's men.

From Norway, in Norwegian

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
